	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scis, colendissime frater, quanta sint dissidia inter Lutheranos per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxoniam</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2562" cert="high">Prussiam</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l743" cert="high">Pomeraniam</placeName> et vicinas gentes.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ideo vero viri boni ex illis partibus et ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Dania</placeName> denique non semel a me afflagitarunt precibus, ut praeteritis nominibus diversa docentium, ut omissis iurgiis et convitiis simpliciter et ordine iusto seu methodico hoc iustificationis fidei et operum negotium tractem, maxime vero dissimulem, necubi appareat propter ista dissidia, sed propter papistas, communes hostes, scripta esse, praefigam autem apologiam, quam praefixi ad serenissimum <persName type="auto_name" ref="p18449">Danie regem</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Parui illorum precibus et placide satis, opinor, tractavi hanc causam.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominum ora, ut meis laboribus benedicat et pacem ecclesiarum componat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quia vero tu ex primis es, quos singulariter amo et participem semper feci consiliorum meorum et laborum, rursus hoc ad te exemplum mitto.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam nec tibi nec aliis piis displiceat.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Simul oro, ut pro me dominum preceris, me et meos tibi habeas commendatos.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1057">Fuchsio</persName> omnia imprecare felicia.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fratris morbus sic fere more suo pergit, quamvis aliquando mitescant dolores, aliquando recurrant.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salvus sit <persName ref="p4868" cert="high">Iacobus Funcklius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7879">Wittenbachius</persName>, d. <persName ref="p4188" cert="high">Valerius</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Göuffi.</note>, omnes viri boni.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vive et vale aeternum.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es ist ein ungrüchliche straas, bekumm schwarlich bottschafft.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Gallus</persName> sollicite colligit militem in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName>, ut obsidione liberet fanum S. Florentii in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2801" cert="high">Corsica</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Germaniae omnia sic sunt convulsa, ut pene desperaverim.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 5. februarii 1554.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimmo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Bienenensis</placeName> ecclesiae fido pastori, domino et fratri colendo suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Byell</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
